## **APPROVAL CONTINGENT ON**

1. Address all 7 critical issues in progress.txt before starting SP_0007.0
2. Create new task SP_0006.5 for JSON Logic arithmetic
3. Reorder SP_0007.x tasks per Issue #5
4. Update SP_0007.0 deliverable to include error handling spec

Once these are addressed, the architecture will be **production-ready**.

